      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. That's a bit more balanced, but I want to make sure the students don't walk away thinking the opposition has a valid leg to stand on. Could you add a part explaining why the \"original intent\" argument is often seen as an outdated or flawed way to look at the Constitution in a modern context? I really want to show them why the progressive interpretation is the more logical one for today's world.",
